text: Hanzlík (feminine Hanzlíková) is a Czech surname. Notable people with this name include: * Bill Hanzlik (born 1957), American basketball player and coach * Jan Hanzlík (born 1982), Czech ice hockey player * Jiří Hanzlík (born 1974), Czech ice hockey player * Michaela Lucie Hanzlíková, Czech figure skater * Steffi Hanzlik, German skeleton racer ==See also== *3257 Hanzlík, a main belt asteroid Category:Czech-language surnames
